      "writtenOn": "2015-09-16T22:38:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think\n\n[AndroidEmu] + [QEMU1 glue] + [QEMU1] \u003d\u003d [Classic emulator]\n\nis more accurate. Every line of code should have a home in the diagram.\n\nIt should also be clear that [QEMU1 glue] is the only one that depends on AndroidEmu and QEMU1, and there should be no dependency between AndroidEmu and QEMU1/QEMU2, in principle.",
