        "id": 1000411
      },
      "writtenOn": "2015-09-17T08:06:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah, this needs clarification as well. In a nutshell:\n\n  external/qemu/android/telephony: will be part of AndroidEmu\n  external/qemu/telephony/: will be part of QEMU1 glue.\n\nFact is that external/qemu/telephony will very likely move\nto external/qemu/android-qemu1/ which will be the location of all the glue code.",
      "parentUuid": "246d66b4_793ddff0",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 97,
        "startChar": 27,
