      "writtenOn": "2015-09-17T08:06:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In a nutshell, it doesn\u0027t include \"qemu-common.h\", or any other QEMU-specific header (e.g. any stuff from \"hw/...\"). Also shall include stuff from \"android/...\" (after moving all the rest into \"android-qemu1/\").\n \nIt\u0027s not possible to give \"reasonable timeframes\" at the moment so I won\u0027t try.",
      "parentUuid": "64383eb1_56a1ea62",
